    "The LLM-based surrogate user learns the real user's preferences and decides to employ attribute-oriented tools to explore areas of items.This process leads to a broad view of items, which, in turn, leads to the successful retrieval of the target item.",
    "It is important to note that the areas representing different attributeoriented items that are retrieved according to a specific attribute may contain overlapping elements.",
